    "Description": "ABOUT THE JOB\nmicroTech Protection Services need a professional to eliminate several creatures of various species. This is a preventative measure to ensure their population size doesn\u2019t increase beyond acceptable parameters.\n\nRESPONSIBILITIES\n\u2022 Provide own transportation. \n\u2022 Locate the target species on ~mission(Location).\n\u2022 Use force as necessary to eliminate the animals.\n\nMINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 1 year of relevant mercenary and/or security experience.\n\u2022 Access to combat equipment.\n\u2022 Available for immediate deployment.\n\nPREFERRED QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Experience with extermination.\n\nFor more information on the animals in question, refer to \"The Guide to Stanton Wildlife\" in your Journal.",
